rComments: To do decent you have to work extra hard and write down EVERY SINGLE THING HE SAYS. The content is not hard but he is a really tough marker and does not want you to succeed. He can be funny during lectures but he is very arrogant towards students (gets annoyed when we ask him for help...). He will do the bare minimum to help you.

Not a bad prof but is arrogant. He is not organized. His power point are very basic and he does not understand technology. His lecture are very long, but he can be funny sometimes. This class does have a group project. His exams are very basic, like name theses things, identify this, explain why this happens, give a situation for this concept.

Really loved Lajoie! He's a great lecturer and I thought it was really nice that we only had a midterm, a presentation and a final. His midterm and final were fair, but I thought that the final had a few specific questions I didn't know the answer to. He's a tough grader for the exams, but easy going for the presentation.
Funny Guy, does well to explain and answer questions.
hes is really funny, but tough grader.
